待”规则。</p>"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "ikvcvo2cckb7jb", "subject": "向勇老师课堂问答peterson算法三个线程的反例", "created": "2016-04-25T12:56:41Z", "content": "<p>线程0&#xff0c;1&#xff0c;2</p>\n<p>turn=1&#xff0c;flag[1]=false&#xff0c;flag[0] = true&#xff0c;flag[2] = true</p>\n<p>在线程T0和T2的peterson算法实现中&#xff0c;只要flag[j]=true和turn=j任意一个不满足&#xff0c;&#xff08;理论上&#xff09;T0&#xff0c;T2就可以进入临界区。由前面假设可得&#xff0c;flag[1] = false&#xff0c;此时while(flag[j]&amp;&amp;turn==j)不足以阻塞T0,T2&#xff0c;两个线程都满足进入临界区的条件&#xff0c;不满足临界区的“忙则等待”规则。</p>"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "ikvcvo2cckb7jb", "subject": "向勇老师课堂问答peterson算法三个线程的反例", "created": "2016-04-25T12:55:15Z", "content": "<p>线程0&#xff0c;1&#xff0c;2</p>\n<p>turn=1&#xff0c;flag[1]=false&#xff0c;flag[0] = true&#xff0c;flag[2] = true</p>\n<p>在线程T0和T2的peterson算法实现中&#xff0c;只要flag[j]=true和turn=j任意一个不满足&#xff0c;&#xff08;理论上&#xff09;T0&#xff0c;T2就可以进入临界区。由前面假设可得&#xff0c;flag[1] = false&#xff0c;此时while(flag[j]&amp;&amp;turn==j)不足以阻塞T0,T2&#xff0c;两个线程都妈祖进入临界区的条件&#xff0c;不满足临界区的“忙则等待”规则。</p>"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "ikvcvo2cckb7jb", "subject": "向勇老师课堂问答peterson算法三个线程的反例", "created": "2016-04-25T12:48:05Z", "content": "<p>线程0&#xff0c;1&#xff0c;2</p>\n<p>turn=1&#xff0c;flag[1]=true</p>\n<p>while(flag[j]&amp;&amp;turn==j)不足以阻塞T0,T2&#xff0c;不满足临界区的“忙则等待”规则。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>#2013011302</p>"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "ikvcvo2cckb7jb", "subject": "向勇老师课堂问答peterson算法三个线程的反例", "created": "2016-04-25T12:44:59Z", "content": "<p>线程0&#xff0c;1&#xff0c;2</p>\n<p>turn=1&#xff0c;flag[1]=true</p>\n<p>在线程T0和T2的peterson算法实现中&#xff0c;只要flag[j]=1和turn=j任意一个不满足&#xff0c;&#xff08;理论上&#xff09;T0&#xff0c;T2就可以进入临界区。此时while(flag[j]&amp;&amp;turn==j)不足以阻塞T0,T2&#xff0c;不满足临界区的“忙则等待”规则。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>#2013011302</p>"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "subject": "向勇老师课堂问答peterson算法三个进程的反例", "created": "2016-04-25T08:15:33Z", "content": "<p>进程0&#xff0c;1&#xff0c;2</p>\n<p>turn=1&#xff0c;flag[1]=true</p>\n<p>则while(flag[j]&amp;&amp;turn==j)不足以阻塞T0,T2</p>\n<p>不满足忙则等待</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>#2013011302</p>"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "ikvcvo2cckb